"{\"uid\": \"glassmagazine.com-news-2024-bendheim-installs-mural-olympic-runner-jesse-owens\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Jesse Owens raced to Olympic glory nearly 90 years ago, but his performance in Berlin in 1936 remains indelibly etched in the minds ofBendheimemployees via a digitally printed backlit glass mural at the company's headquarters in Wayne, New Jersey.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesse_Owens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.549276700759638e-36, \"text\": \"Jesse Owens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesse_Owens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesse_Owens\"}, {\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 34, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Glory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic glory\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Glory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Glory\"}, {\"begin\": 79, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"score\": 0.9999090978174274, \"rank\": 4.520399999720088e-05, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"score\": 0.9999960475643894, \"rank\": 2.640210138631715e-06, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The image of Owens-8 feet high and 15 feet wide-is the first thing people see when entering the headquarters of the architectural glass manufacturer.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The wall includes four panels of digitally printed glass that combine to create the overall image.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The glass is installed with Bendheim's TurnKey\\u00a0Fusion Light Wall system, which uses petite clips to capture the glass, eliminating the need for adhesives or expensive glass drilling.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fusion_power\", \"score\": 0.7884949942249037, \"rank\": 0.135377375718081, \"text\": \"Fusion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fusion_power\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fusion_power\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The project captures Owens as he competes en route to four gold medals at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won individual gold medals in the 100 and 200 meters and long jump.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also ran on the victorious 4 x 100-meter relay.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Berlin Games were held amid a politically charged atmosphere, coming just three years after Adolf Hitler was appointed chancellor of Germany.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9999999999552074, \"rank\": 4.43361696635104e-11, \"text\": \"Adolf Hitler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\"}, {\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9422196509049783, \"rank\": 0.06128428279634872, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The wall acts as a representation of values that Jesse's performance symbolized, including bravery, optimism and teamwork,\\\" Bendheim President Donald Jayson says.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We hope that the mural inspires both our team and visitors alike.\\\"\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The mural's significance takes on added importance amid the Summer Olympics currently underway in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995019512756, \"rank\": 4.980489154455004e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9304288056927047, \"rank\": 0.03466507872203159, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saturday, August 3, will mark the 88th anniversary of Owens' victory in the 100-meter dash at the Berlin Olympics.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"National Glass Association344 Maple Ave WestUnit 272Vienna, VA 22180703/442-4890  Contact us      \\u00a9 National Glass Association.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Glass_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Glass Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Glass_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Glass_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.Privacy Policy\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}]}"